          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst School. Worst Administration\nWorst rules and regulations\nIt’s totally a place for looting parents.\n1) Teachers keep changing. 3-4 times in a single year\n2) Sports facility : Zero\n3) Coach : No idea\n4) Other Facilities: Minimal\n5) Transport : Worst. They even ask kids to cross roads by themselves as they mostly don’t have helper, only driver &\nWhen you go to complain to the dean or principal, they take sides of their driver only and asked us to look for other options.\n6) They even charge transport fee for vacation month and even doesn’t give option to withdraw transport in last 3 months.\n7) Finance person gave clear warning/DHAMKI that “Agar TC chaiye to transport complete 12 months ka dena padega”\n\nSo I decided to withdraw my child from this pathetic institution.\n\nMy suggestion don’t fall in trap of these money makers, no development of your child in terms of athletics, personality, communication or extra curriculum.",
